title: Properties of Materials Laboratory
description: Laboratory sequence illustrating topics covered in course 145. One two-hour laboratory per week.

pre_req_data.text: Prerequisite(s): PHYS 5A and PHYS 5L, PHYS 5B and PHYS 5M, and PHYS 5C and 5N; or PHYS 6A and PHYS 6L, PHYS 6B and PHYS 6M, and PHYS 6C and PHYS 6N. Concurrent enrollment in ECE 102 is required.

class_notes: Concurrent enrollment in ECE 102 is required. Enroll in lab and associated secondary lab.
